name: Mens Handmade Beaded Sterling Silver Tube Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Sterling Silver Tube Necklace

This classic designed mens necklace has sterling silver tube beads with randomly drilled holes complemented by brown Jasper stone tubes and Bronzite rondelles.  Measures 19 1/2" with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp and two sterling rondelles.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Blackstone and Obsidian
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Blackstone and  Obsidian

The Blackstone bamboo-shaped beads in this masculine bracelet are teamed with round black Obsidian beads with a gray snowflake-like coloring. Also included are silver-toned metal disc beads and two decorative metal spacer beads.  This men's bracelet measures 8 3/4" long ending with a metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: PMC Pendant Necklace - Drops of Lavender
description:
PMC Pendant Necklace - Drops of Lavender



This small 1 ¼” X 5/8” PMC pendant, handcrafted in the Keiden Designs studio, is hand textured and layered with a linear design down the center that features droplets of lavender acrylic inlay. This is a highly polished piece with a textured back mounted on a sterling  snake chain in 16", 18" or 20" in length.  Please choose desired length before checking out.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bali, Bone and Gemstones
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bali, Bone and Gemstones

The three sterling silver oval beads in this masculine necklace were handmade by silver artisans in Bali India.  Complementing these beads are black bone hairpipe, black Onyx rounds and contrasting yellow Turquoise rondelle shaped beads.  This classic mens beaded necklace measures 19" and has a metal hook and eye clasp.

name: Ladies Handmade Beaded Turquoise Disk Necklace
description:
Ladies Handmade Beaded Turquoise Disk Necklace

This lovely strand of stablized Turquoise beads are graduated in size.  Larger disk beads in the front; smaller beads at the back for comfortable wear.  The Turquoise beads are a deep medium blue in color with similar in color smaller round Turquoise beads to separate each disk bead.  This feminine necklace measures approximately 18 1/2" and has a silver-toned metal decorative toggle clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock and Black Coral
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock and Black Coral

The natural lava rock in this beaded necklace, are formated from volcanic matter and include naturally-formed voids and irregular surfaces, making each bead unique.  The color of these barrel-shaped tube beads are a natural off-white, complementing the Black Coral rondell-shaped beads.  The length of this natrual earthy-style men's necklace is 20 3/4" and concludes with a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

Check out the matching bracelet on the "Mens Beaded Bracelet" page.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Tiger Eye Bracelet
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Tiger Eye Bracelet

Tiger-eye tube beads with contrasting golden and brown bands of color and Blackstone rondelle shaped beads make up this casual mens gemstone bracelet.  Measures 8 1/2" long with a brass lobster claw clasp and jumpring along with two decorative brass beads.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Agate Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Agate Necklace

These unusual Agate beads are barrel-shaped in a medium brown with a white band through the center. Complementing these unique beads are white bone round beads.  Measures 20" long with a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: PMC Necklace - Leaf Design Pure Silver PMC Pendant
description:
Handmade Pure Silver Jewelry - PMC Necklace - Leaf Design Pure Silver PMC Pendant

PMC pendant pure silver (99.9%) with patina finish;  1 1/4" long by 7/8" wide with raised etched leaf design.  Pendant hangs from a  black leather cord with a sterling lobster claw clasp and 2 1/2" metal chain, making the length adjustable from 19 1/2"  to 22".

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Kambaba Jasper and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Kambaba Jasper and Blackstone

The Kambaba Jasper gemstone tubes in this mens necklace are from South Africa and have deep rich patterns of moss green with patterns of medium and light green.  Not to be outdone are these interesting "bamboo shaped" Blackstone beads in a rich black opaque color.  Also complementing the piece are Jet disc beads.  Measures 20" long and ends with two brass colored decorative beads and a brass lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: PMC Necklace - Vintage Oval Floral Necklace PMC Pendant
description:
PMC Necklace - Vintage Oval Floral Necklace PMC Pendant

An intricate floral design with subtle acrylic inlay highlights of green, purple and blue. This is a Keiden Designs handcrafted original one of a kind piece.  The bail is ¼” wide and highly polished and the back has a hammered texture.  Select either a 16" or !8" sterling silver neck wire or 16", 18" or 20" sterling silver snake chain.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Red Jasper and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Red Jasper and Blackstone

The Red Jasper gemstones in this mens bracelet are a deep brick red color with bands of cream, gray and tan.  The Blackstone beads are a bamboo shape with metal disc beads that flank each of the Blackstone beads enhancing their deep opaque black color.  Measures 8 1/2" with two decorative silver-toned beads and a pewter rope style toggle clasp.  This mens bracelet is a match for the handmade beaded Red Jasper and Blackstone necklace.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Jasper Stone and Black Onyx
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Jasper Stone and Black Onyx

These rondelle-shaped brownish-red Jasper Stone beads are a nice contrast to the round and barrel-shaped Black Onyx beads.  The finish on the Black Onyx beads are a frosted matte giving this masculine necklace a unique look.  Also included are metal disc beads complementing the Jasper beads.  Measures 20 3/4" and concludes with a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Blackstone and Magnesite
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Blackstone and Magnesite

Bamboo-shaped Blackstone beads and complementary Magnesite beads make up this mens beaded necklace with gunmetal spacer beads throughout.  Measures 19 and 3/4" and concludes with a silver-toned metal barrel-shaped screw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Tiger-eye Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Tiger-eye Necklace

Tiger-eye tube beads - approximately a 1/2" long -are teamed with Czech glass shell-like rondelles and brass disc-shaped beads.  This casual men's necklace measures 19 3/4" in length and has a brass lobster claw closure with matching jumpring.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock and Turquoise
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock and Turquoise

The black, natural lava rock in this beaded necklace, are formated from volcanic matter and include naturally-formed voids and irregular surfaces, making each bead unique. Teamed with the  Lava Rock are Turquoise disc beads with several shades of turquoise blue and green, including areas of brown matrix throughout.  Down to earth and natural, this masculine beaded necklace measures 20 and 3/4" ending with a natural brass lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Black Onyx Necklace
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Black Onyx Necklace

This elegant womens necklace has natural black onyx beads in various shapes and sizes.  Large flat octagon-shape, round tubes and small and medium round beads in a high-gloss black color.  The four unusual black agate puffed oval beads with natural bandings of burnt orange, make this a unique and interesting piece of jewelry.  Worn long this womens necklace measures 32 1/2"  including the silver-toned metal chain and sterling spring ring clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Snowflake Obsidian and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Snowflake Obsidian and Blackstone

These interesting Snowflake Obsidian tube-shaped beads make this masculine beaded necklace unique.  Snowflake Obsidian is volcanic glass and the snowflake appearance is produced by internal crystallites that form as the lava cools quickly.  Enhancing the look of the tube beads are round and bamboo shaped Blackstone beads.  The length measures 20 1/2" with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: PMC Pendant Necklace - Rock Star
description:
PMC Pendant Necklace - Rock Star


The 1 1/8” PMC pendant necklace has a small bail mounted on the back and looks great on this 2 1/2mm Italian leather cord.  The hand carved abstract star surrounding the center has a patina finish.  Measures 20" long and has a sterling silver hook and eye
clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Czech Glass and Pearls
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Czech Glass and Pearls

Peridot Czech glass teardrop and round-shaped beads with cream and maize colored fresh-water pearls are handwired to a natural brass chain giving this women's dangle bracelet a modern style.  The unique natural brass toggle clasp has a floral design that completes this pretty and feminine piece. Measures 7 and 1/4".

name: Womens Handmade Lacquered Wood Necklace
description:
Womens Handmade Lacquered Wood Necklace

The beads in this woman's necklace are black wood wrapped in mesh and then lacquered.  The size of these uniqued beads are about 14mm but they are lightweight.  Other elements in this necklace are black faceted glass rondelles with gold-tone metal spacer beads.  Concludes with an imitation suede cord and gold-toned lobster claw clasp and a 2 1/4" extension chain.  Measures 18 1/2" - 21".

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - The Scorpion
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - The Scorpion

Silver-toned metal square beads with raised scorpion design are the focal point in this unique mens bracelet.  Complementing the "scorpion" beads are disc-shaped Turquoise beads with blends of blue, green, brown, and tan  along with Black Onyx round beads in a matte finish.  Measures 8 3/4" and finishes with two sterling silver rondelles and a antiqued silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and a sterling silver jumpring with a silver-toned metal charm.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Whimsical Butterfly
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Whimsical Butterfly

The focal piece of this women's beaded necklace is a hand-carved butterfly pendant made from the gemstone Magnesite.  Also included in this whimsical piece of jewelry are Jasper stone round beads in deep earthy colors of sienna and light and dark browns.  The beads are wired to a natural antiqued bronze brass chain with a natrual brass lobster claw clasp.
The necklace is worn long measuring 24 1/2".  The pendant drop measures 5" from the decorative brass filligree bead to the end of the tassel chains.  

This necklace also comes with a matching pair of earrings that can be viewed in picture two.  The earrings drop 1 3/4" from  all natural brass earwires.

name: Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fine Art Porcelain Beads
description:
Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fine Art Porcelain Beads

A special low-fire technique gives these Fine art porcelain beads a smooth, modern style.  The earthy maize colored tube beads and the antiqued blue round beads combine together giving this necklace a Southwestern appeal.  Measures 18 3/4"  long with a metal barrel clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Copper Heart
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Copper Heart

Copper has always been known for its healing properties and this womens beaded bracelet will add style to your wrist as well.  The decorative heart clasp is magnetic, allowing for easy off/on wear.  The pretty glass beads are a teal green set in copper square beads.  Complementing each beaded station are tiny copper heart-shaped beads.  Measures 7 3/4 inches.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Black Onyx and Red Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Black Onyx and Red Jasper

These brick red  Jasper stone tube-shaped beads have swirls and crackles of deep brown, black and gray.  Complementing the Jasper stones are Black Onyx round beads in a deep black color with a matte finish.  Also included in this men's necklace are Red Jasper rondelles and silver-toned metal disc beads. Measures 20 3/4" long with a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring and two decorative silver-toned metal beads.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper

Picture Jasper is named for its striking patterns that resemble landscapes of dry, mountainous regions.  These Jasper gemstone beads in this mens necklace have both tube and rondelle shape with tan, cream and brown colors naturallly blended in swirls and mottled designs to create a very distintive look.  Other beads complementing the Jasper stones are Bronzite rondelles and two decorative silver-toned metal beads.  Measures 20 1/4" long and concludes with a silver-toned lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: PMC Necklace - Acrylic Swirl PMC Pendant
description:
Handmade Pure Silver Jewelry - PMC Necklace - Acrylic Swirl PMC Pendant

PMC pendant (99.9 silver), measures 1 3/4" long and 3/4" wide with lavender and rose acrylic swirl inlaid.  Pendant hangs on your choice of three different sizes of sterling silver snake chains or 2 sizes of neckwires.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Antiqued Pewter and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Antiqued Pewter and Blackstone

These antiqued pewter tube beads are handcut in a coil design giving this mens beaded necklace its masculine appeal.  Also included are Blackstone tubes in a satiny, moderate gloss polish and tiny Red Jasper gemstones.  Measures 19" in length and concludes with two silver-toned metal beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Black Obsidian and Turquoise
description:
Mens Handmade Beadd Necklace - Black Obsidian and Turquoise

This men's beaded necklace has Black Obsidian twisted tube beads in an obaque black color with swirls of light gray and tan.  Complementing the Obsidian beads are Turquoise rondelle-shaped beads in a light blue.  Also included in this men's beaded necklace are square-shaped silver-toned metal beads. Measures 18 3/4" with a sterling lobster claw clasp and metal jumpring.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picasso Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picasso Jasper

Like a Picasso painting, this unique masculine beaded necklace has an abstract and modernistic look.  The four-sided tube beads and matching round beads are grey in color with steaks of black, with silver-toned metal disc beads throughout adding to the necklace's distinctive look.  Measures 19" long concluding with two square shaped silver-toned metal beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: Men's Handmade Beaded Necklace - Hematite and Red Jasper
description:
Men's Handmade Beaded Necklace - Hematite and Red Jasper

Hematite beads in round, rondelle shaped and twisted tubes with a large Hematite nugget bead, take center stage in this stylish men's necklace. Red Jasper tube beads in a brick red with swirls of gray and cream bring out the luster in the Hematite beads.  Measures 21 1/4" concluding with a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

Check out the coordinating Hematite stretch bracelet on the mens beaded bracelet page.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Picasso Jasper Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Picasso Jasper Necklace

The gemstones in this handmade beaded necklace are Black Onyx  in a matte finish with metal discs between each bead; and Picasso Jasper barrel shaped beads. These Picasso Jasper gemstones are unusual and unique with their gray to cream background with swirls of black.  Each bead is different from the other making this masculine necklace one of a kind.  Measures 19 1/2" and concludes with two sterling silver rondelle-shaped beads and a sterling silver "s" shaped lobster claw clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Black Sea Glass
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Black Sea Glass

This womens beaded necklace consists of black and white frosted Sea Glass in round and disc shaped nuggets. Each bead is flanked by silver metal beads and black seed beads. Attached to a black suede cord, this stylish necklace measures 25" long with a 3 3/4" silver extension chain and lobster clasw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Snowflake Obsidian and Picasso Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Snowflake Obsidian and Picasso Jasper

These Jasper gemstones called "Picasso" have wide streaks of black and grey giving these rectangular beads an abstract and modernistic look.  The complementary Obsidian beads have a "snowflake" look because of the internal crystallite formations. Also included in this mens necklace are silver-toned metal disc beads that nicely offset the Jasper rectangular tube beads.  Measures 19" long ending with 2 silver-toned metal round beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp with jumpring.

name: Handmade Beaded Copper and Turquoise Bohemian Style Necklace
description:
Handmade Beaded Copper and Turquoise Bohemian Style Necklace

Antique copper pendant with stamped vintage design hangs 2 1/4" from a 19 1/2" strand of Turquoise, Blue Lapis and Gold Leaf Agate beads.
Other elements in this women's beaded necklace are copper bead caps, topaz colored crystals and fancy copper large link chain with a square shaped copper toggle clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Turquoise Breeze
description:
Womens Handmande Beaded Necklace - Turquoise Breeze

Pretty greenish-blue Turquoise gemstones in nuggets and chips make this womens beaded necklace a must have for spring and summer.  The off-white bone bead long tubes and matching round beads complement these nice looking Turquoise beads. Also included are white wood triangular-shaped beads that add interest and uniqueness to this lovely piece.  Measures 24" with a sterling 1 3/4" extension chain with lobster claw clasp.  Also comes with a matching pair of earrings on sterling silver earwires shown in image #2.

name: Women's Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picasso Jasper and Obsidian
description:
Women's Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picasso Jasper and Obsidian

These Picasso Jasper marquis-style gemstone beads, with wide streaks and narrow veins of black, taupe, grey and white, are the focus of this bib-style necklace.  Each of these beads measures 1 and 1/8" and are strung with complementing Picasso Jasper rondelle shaped beads and tiny Obsidian round beads. This stylish and modernistic necklace has a sterling silver lobster claw clasp and measures 19" with a 2 3/4" extension chain.

name: Men's Hematite Stretch Bracelet
description:
Men's Hematite Stretch Bracelet

This men's stretch bracelet is made up of black lustrous Hematite beads in shapes of round, twisted tube and disc.  Measures 8 1/2" and is a perfect coordinate for the Men's Hematite and Red Jasper tube necklace.

name: Handmade Beaded Youth  Necklace - Picture Jasper and Bronzite
description:
Handmade Beaded Yoouth Necklace - Picture Jasper and Bronzite

Picture jasper is named for its striking patterns that resemble the landscapes of dry, mountainous regions. These short-tubed beads have tan and brown and cream coloring and are complemented by Bronzite rondelle-shaped beads in shades of brown.  These beads in this Youth necklace are smaller than the typical "mens style necklace" making it an appropriate choice for the younger male.  Measures 15 1/2" with a silver-toned hook and eye clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone Necklace
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone Necklace

Red Creek and Fancy Jasper stones in shapes of round, rondelle and teardrop are accented by natural brass washer style beads and a large linked natural brass chain.  The natural brass toggle clasp is leaf style with a floral designed toggle bar. Measures 21".

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Red Jasper Pendant Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Red Jasper Pendant Necklace

The "Celtic Knot" pewter pendant in this mens necklace hangs from a strand of Red Jasper square-shaped gemstones and Black Onyx round beads.  The pendant measures 1" in length and 7/8" in width. The  necklace measures 20" with a 1 3/4" entension chain making the overall length from 20" to 21 3/4".  The closure is a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Wood and Agate Stretch Bracelet
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Wood and Agate Stretch Bracelet

These unique white-banded Agate beads team with wood round and disc beads to create a simple yet contemporary look.  Easy off and on stretch bracelet measures 8".  Complements the mens "Agate and Wood" necklace on the mens beaded necklace page.

name: Men's Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone and Bone Bead Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone and Bone Bead Necklace

Natural Bone barrel-shaped beads and red variegated Jasper gemstones team together with a black Lava Rock focal bead to make this classic style men's beaded necklace unique.  The Bone tube beads are handcut and dyed black and the Jasper stones are a brownish red with cream and light brown variegations throughout.  The large Lava Rock tube bead is flanked by two silver metal disc beads.  This masculine necklace measures 20" and has an antiqued silver metal lobster claw clasp and 2 decorative metal beads. Matching bracelet is sold separately and can be viewed on the "men's beaded bracelet page".

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Lava Rock and Black Coral
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Lava Rock and Black Coral

The natural lava rock in this beaded necklace, are formated from volcanic matter and include naturally-formed voids and irregular surfaces, making each bead unique. Teamed with Black Coral rondelle-shaped beads, these off-white colored barrel shaped beads offer a earthy style and rugged appearance.  Measures 8 1/2" and strung on stretch elastic. 
Check out the matching necklace on the"Mens Beaded Bracelet" page.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Carved Bone Bead and Wood
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Carved Bone Bead and Wood

These carved Bone bead tubes are teamed with wood and bone disc-shaped beads.  Strung on a coated braided cotton cord this casual necklace measures 19 1/2" long and has a handmade beaded toggle clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Dalmatian Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Dalmatian Jasper

Dalmatian Jasper stones have a distinct pattern of sporadic black spots on a opaque and spotted tawny, cream-colored base.  These rondelle-shaped beads are teamed with a large marquise style natural "Jet" bead in a solid opaque black color.  Complementing the Jet bead are two sterling silver disc beads and two Black onyx rounds.  Measures approximately 18 3/4" and concludes with two sterling silver rondelle-shaped beads and a silver metal-toned lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Blackstone and Jasper
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Blackstone and Jasper

These bamboo-shaped Blackstone beads are a 1/2" long with a semi-matte finish and are flanked by silver-tone metal disc beads.  Complementing the Blackstone beads are rondelle-shaped Jasper gemstones, in variegated colors of black, gray, cream and tan.  Measures 19 3/4" and finishes with two sterling rondelle shaped beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp and jumpring.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Chrysolite and Lava Rock
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Chrysolite and Lava Rock

These unusual Chrysolite tube beads in a moss green color have flecks of black and turquoise.  Black Lava Rock beads-that have been  formated from volcanic matter - team nicely with the black coconut heishi beads. This earthy style necklace measures 19 1/4" with two decorative silver-toned metal beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Natural Agate and Carnelian
description:
Womens Handmade  Beaded Necklace - Natural Agate and Carnelian

These eye-catching Agate beads in warm shades of butterscotch and amber, are teamed with large and smaller faceted round Carnelian beads. Measures 16 1/2" with an 3" sterling silver extension chain and lobster claw clasp giving the overall length to 19".

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Red Jasper and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Red Jasper and Blackstone

These Red Jasper gemstones are a deep brick red color with bands of cream, gray and tan.  The Blackstone beads are a bamboo shape that adds a uniqueness to this classic-style mens necklace.  Silver-toned metal disc beads flank each of the Blackstone beads enhancing their deep opaque black color.  Measures 18 1/2" concluding with two siver-toned metal beads and a silver-toned metal swivel lobster claw clasp.

This necklace also has a matching bracelet that can be viewed by clicking on the "mens handmade beaded bracelet page".

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fresh-Water Pearls with Silver Heart Pendant
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fresh Water Pearls with Silver Heart Pendant


This silver handmade heart pendant, created by Hill Tribes artisans of Thailand, is of a higher purity than 92.5% sterling silver and will not tarnish as readily.  Measuring about an inch in diameter, this unique pendant hangs nicely from a strand of long black stick-shaped fresh-water pearls in a baroque style along with Garnet round beads and black Swarovski crystal bicone beads.  The closure is a sterling silver tab-lock style with stamped design.  This romantic piece of jewelry measures approximately 20" and will surely become a classic piece to add to your jewelry collection.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Agate and Tiger-eye
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Agate and Tiger-eye

No bead is as creatively designed by nature than these unusual and unique gemstones.  Large and chunky, these beads have background colors of translucent moss green, tan and brown with flecks and swirls of cream.  Tiny Tiger-eye and natural shell beads combine together with the Agate to make a truly special piece of jewelry.  The necklace is long, measuring 30" with a 2" sterling silver extension chain.  The clasp is a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Fossil Stone and Jasper Tube Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Fossil Stone and Jasper Tube Necklace

Modern Fossil stone tube beads in a gray/tan background with flecks of cream and red team nicely with the short tubular brick red Jasper stone beads with background colors of cream and gray. Complementing the tube beads are brick red Jasper round beads, modern Fossil rondelle shaped beads and sterling silver disk beads that accentuate the Jasper tubes. Measures approx. 19" in length and has a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper and Bone Bead
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper and Bone Bead

Picture Jasper is named for its striking patterns that resemble the  landscapes of dry, mountainous regions. The Jasper stone beads in this mens necklace have tan and brown colors naturally blended in swirls and mottled designs to create a very distinctive look.  Complementing the Jasper stones are natural Bone heishi style beads.  Measures 201/2"with a silver-toned metal hook and eye clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone and Bone Bead Bracelet
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone and Bone Bead Bracelet

This mens stretch bracelet is a match for the "Mens Beaded Jasper Stone and Bone Bead Necklace.  Black Bone bead barrel-shaped tubes and red variegated Jasper Stone rondelles are the matching beads for the necklace.  Measures 8 1/4" and is strung on elastic cord eliminating the need for a clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Bone Bead Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Bone Bead Necklace 

This unique casual mens necklace of bone bead in different shapes and sizes has two handcrafted bone bead tubes as the focal point of the necklace along with an antiqued-color handcrafted round bone bead  in the center of the two tubes. The disc beads are bone and dyed a cool ocean blue with additional antiqued-colored round beads throughout the strand with silver-toned metal beads hugging each bone bead.  Lightweight and earthy in style this mens necklace measures 19" and has a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Red Creek Jasper Stone Necklace
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Red Creek Jasper Stone Necklace

These large (10mm) Jasper Stone rondelle shaped beads, called Red Creek", have bands and swirls of red, brown, and lled "greentones with both dark and pale inclusions.  Also included in this unique necklace are gunmetal puffed rondelles with a decorative beaded band around the middle and a gunmetal chain with an antiqued metal toggle clasp.  Measures 19 inches.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Smokey Quartz and Glass
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Smokey Quartz and Glass

Dangling from a silver-toned metal chain are Smokey Quartz round beads with silver-toned metal beadcaps in a floral design.  Along with the Smokey Quartz beads are black glass Czech beads in oblong drops and rounds.  Each bead is handwired to the chain creating a very delicate looking woman's necklace measuring 17 1/2" with a sterling spring ring clasp. Also included is a matching pair of earrings.  To view earrings click on number 2 at bottom of picture.

name: Handmade Beaded Youth Necklace - Red Jasper Stone and Jet
description:
Handmade Beaded Youth Necklace - Red Jasper Stone and Jet

These Red Jasper stone tube beads - with colors of brick red, cream and gray - are strikingly contrasted with opaque black Jet beads, found in the coal mines of northern China.  The lightness of this necklace make it an appropriate choice for the younger male.  Measures 15 1/4" with a silver-toned metal hook and eye clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead and Wood
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead and Wood

This fun necklace is made of Bone disc-shaped bone beads and large wood beads with printed designs.  The bone beads are a natural off-white and the wood beads have colors ranging from beige to reddish oranges and yellows.  This casual piece measures
25" long and lays just above the cleavage.  Strung on durable cotton cording with a silver-toned metal hook and eye clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone Bracelet
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Jasper Stone Bracelet

 The Jasper gemstones in this mens stretch bracelet are a deep brick red with occasional grey, green and cream streaks and swirls.
Metal disc beads and decorative silver-toned metal beads team nicely with the Jasper Stones.   Measures 8 1/4".

name: Ladies Handmade Beaded Chunky Bracelet - Agate and Sterling Silver
description:
Ladies Handmade Beaded Chunky Bracelet - Agate and Sterling Silver

These eye-catching agate beads in large barrel and rondelle shape, range in colors of red, black, brown, with warm golden hues of orange, yellow and green.  Tiny silver spacer beads help enhance the lustrous colors of these vibrant beads while the sterling silver handcrafted Bali flower bead charm adds a artistic look to this classic design. 
Measures 7 3/4" with a large sterling silver "S" shaped lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Art Glass and Bone Bead
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Art Glass and Bone Bead

Taking center stage in this bohemian style masculine necklace, is an art glass oval bead crafted by lampwork artisans.  The black and tan colors of this bead complement nicely the black bone tubes and barrel shaped beads.  Other elements of this piece are black wood disc beads and a sterling silver hook and eye clasp.  Strung on cotton cord for a flexible and soft drape, this necklace measures 20" long.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead Tubes and Jasper Gemstones
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead Tubes and Jasper Gemstones

The tube shaped Bone beads in this mens beaded necklace measure 1" and have great natural beige and cream coloring.  The Jasper gemstone rondelle shaped beads are a mix of white, grey, cream with tan and black swirls of color.  Also included in this mens necklace are silver-toned round metal beads with two sterling rondelle beads.  Measures 19 1/4" long with a silver-toned metal swivel style lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fossil Agate and Blackstone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Fossil Agate and Blackstone

You will be wearing a piece of ancient history with these fossil stone Agate beads.  Made of pieces of broken shell that have rested in a bed of mud for millions of years and then transformed into stone, these unusual tube beads bring a uniqueness to this beaded necklace.  The Blackstone bamboo shaped beads along with Black Onyx round beads complement the Fossil Agate with their variegated colors of shell, coral and black.  The length of this mens necklace is 19 3/4" long with a silver-tone metal lobster claw clasp and two decorative silver-toned metal beads.

name: PMC Necklace - Rosebud Pure Silver PMC Pendant
description:
Handmade Pure Silver Jewelry - PMC Necklace - Rosebud Pure Silver PMC Pendant 

This PMC pendant (99.9 silver) handcrafted in the Keiden Designs studio, has an etched rose design and patina finish.  Pendant measures 1/2' wide and 1 3/4" long and hangs from a 18" leather cord with sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Charm Bracelet
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Charm Bracelet

Blue and white faceted Agate beads with brown striping and marbling; white freshwater pearls, tiny baby blue pearl beads and clear
faceted glass beads are all hand wired to a silver-toned metal round link chain.  The leaf and flower charms are made of pewter.
Measures 7 1/2" long with a silver-toned metal spring ring clasp in a nautical design.

name: Ladies Handmade Beaded Long Necklace
description:
Ladies Handmade Beaded Long Necklace

This long beaded necklace measures 44" long and can be wrapped twice for a double strand necklace or can be worn as one long strand.  The Bohemian style hand-cut and painted glass beads from South Africa are teamed with red coral and dyed yellow Jade along with tiny cream colored shell beads and tiny Red Jasper gemstone  heishi beads.  The clasp is a sterling silver decorative flower hook and eye.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Yellow Turquoise Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Yellow Turqouise Necklace 

These gemstone tube beads are known as "turquoise" because they occur in the same mines and have similar matrix patterns. The
colors range  from yellow to green and black to brown.  Complementing these interesting beads are gray/black shell heishi beads with complementing yellow turquoise rondelles.  This classic design measures 19 3/4" long with two silver-toned metal decorative beads and a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Handmade Beaded Youth Necklace - Jasper Stone and Shell
description:
Handmade Beaded Youth Necklace - Jasper Stone and Shell

The oval tube-shaped tan and brown Jasper Stone beads are called "Picture Jasper"; named for its striking patterns that resemble the landscapes of dry, mountainous regions.  The Jasper gemstones are teamed with natural shell beads in varying colors of brown.  The size and lightness of this necklace make it a great choice for the younger male.  Measures 16" and has a silver-toned metal hook and eye clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone and Buri Beads
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone and Buri Beads

Lightweight and natural, these irregular shaped
tubes are handcarved from the 
seeds of the Phillipine Palm.  The burnt orange and mahogany brown colors are dyed and then lacquered.  Bone bead disc beads complement the tubes giving this necklace a tropical feel.  Measures 19" long and has a silver plate hook and eye clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Gold Leaf Agate Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Gold Leaf Agate Necklace

The Gold Leaf Agate tube beads in this masculine necklace are unique in shape and color.  Six-sided with shades of golden-tan and dark brown, these tube beads are teamed with Gold Leaf Agate round beads and picture Jasper gemstone rondelles.  To complete the design are six large barrel-shaped silver-toned metal  beads.  Measures 19 1/2" long with a sterling silver lobster claw closure.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead and Jasper Stone
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Bone Bead and Jasper Stone

These Black Bone bead tubes are teamed with Red Jasper Stone rondelles.  The Jasper stone is brick red in color with lacy bandings of white quartz, cream and black.  Also included in this masculine necklace are round Black Onyx beads with a matte finish and silver-toned metal discs.  Measures 19" and finishes with two decorative silver metal beads and a silver plated lobster claw clasp.

name: Handmade Beaded Pink Opal Toggle Bracelet
description:
Handmade Beaded Pink Opal Toggle Bracelet

Commonly believed to lift the spirits and bring joy, these natural pink opal beads will do just that.  The pink color ranging from medium to light with occasional inclusions of cream, grey and black mixed into the surface, have an opaque translucency with a smooth polish. Complementing these beads are rose pink fresh water pearls along with tiny sterling silver beads.  The focal of this piece is a handcrafted sterling silver toggle clasp in a leaf design. The length of this feminine bracelet is 7 and 3/4".

name: Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Carnelian and Black Onyx
description:
Womens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Carnelian and Black Onyx
 
Large irregular shaped chunky Carnelian beads and Black Onyx round beads team together to make this striking ladies handmade bracelet.  Measures 7 3/4" long and finishes with a large silver-toned metal leaf design bead and  heart-shaped Black onyx charm.  The closure is a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper Stone with Pewter Pendant
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Picture Jasper Stone with Pewter Pendant

This contemporary piece of jewelry consists of short round tubular shaped Picture Jasper gemstones.  These stones are uniquely different with their picturesque marbled patterns of cream, gray and black.  Complementing these stones are Black Onyx tubular stones with a high sheen and matte colored Black Onyx round beads.  The pewter pendant has a contemporary design that fits nicely with this masculine style necklace.  The closure is a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp with a silver-toned metal chain making the length adjustable from 19" to 21"

name: Handcarved PMC Pendant with Turquoise and Jasper Stone
description:
Handcarved PMC Pendant with Turquoise and Jasper Stone


Primitive style handcarved PMC pendant - 99.9% silver with patina finish.  Blue Turquoise rondelle shaped gemstones along with Jasper gemtones combine to give this necklace its rustic appeal.  The length is 18 1/2" with a sterling silver tab clasp with antique finish.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock with Jagged Dagger Pendant
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Lava Rock with Jagged Dagger Pendant

A strand of Lava Rock beads, formated from volcanic matter, team together with a pewter pendant in a design called "Jagged Dagger".  These black Lava Rock beads have naturally-formed voids and irregular surfaces, making each bead unique.  The pewter pendant is handcrafted and measures 2 1/2" from the bail to the tip of the dagger.  Also included in this masculine necklace, are two metal barrel beads and a metal rope design S-hook clasp. 
The overall length of this necklace is approximately 19 1/2". length.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded "Howling Wolf" Pendant Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded "Howling Wolf" Pendant Necklace

The "Howling Wolf" pewter pendant hangs from a strand of handcarved black and white bone bead tubes in a tribal design.  Black bone rondelles and black onyx rounds complete the necklace.
The pendant measures 1 1/2" x 3/4";  the overall length of this adjustable necklace measures 19 1/2" to 21 1/2" long.  The extension chain is silver metal oval links and the clasp is a silver rhodium lobster claw.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Pewter Pendant With Blackstone Beads
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Pewter Pendant with Blackstone Beads

Teardrop shaped pewter pendant  has a woven design with a black petina background measuring 2" x 1/2"; hangs from a strand of Blackstone faceted-shape tube beads.  Also included are stabilzed Turquoise rondelle shaped beads and silvertoned metal disk beads.  Measures approximately 19" and has a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Faceted Wood Necklace
description:
Mens Handmade Faceted Wood Necklace

This lightweight and comfortable necklace has faceted tube shaped wood beads complemented by African Turquoise disk beads and betel nut rondelles.  Measures 20" and has a silver-toned metal lobster claw clasp.

name: Handmade Gemstone Bead Jewelry - Turquoise and Bali Bead Bracelet
description:
Handmade Gemstone Bead Jewelry - Turquoise and Bali Bead Bracelet

Unique sterling silver beads handmade in Bali India sliding on sterling silver curved tubes, team together with large green turquoise barrel beads with sterling silver bead caps.  Small turquoise round beads and an antique silver pewter toggle clasp in a Bali design complete this unique and eye-catching piece of jewelry.  Measures 8" long.

name: PMC Necklace - Vintage Heart with Sapphire Pure Silver Pendant
description:
Category: Handmade Pure Silver Jewelry

PMC Necklace -  Vintage Heart with Sapphire Pure Silver Pendant

A striking vintage look featuring a fringed heart design with many interesting highlights focusing on a 3mm natural sapphire center mounted.  The bail is attached to the back allowing the pendant to be displayed high if desired.  Your choice of 16" or 18" sterling silver neckwire or snake chain.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Southwest Style
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Southwest Style

Turquoise barrel beads and Pietersite rondelle beads combine together with metal decorative beads.  This masculine bracelet measures 8 1/2" long and concludes with a thick and sturdy textured metal toggle clasp.

name: Handmade Beaded Necklace -Coral Pendant and Pearls
description:
Handmade Beaded Necklace - Coral Pendant and Pearls

Natural freshwater pearls in varying shapes and colors of cream, beige, maize and brown complement the unique handcarved ivory colored Coral flower pendant.  This romantic piece measures 18 1/2" in length with a 2" pendant drop. The closure is a gold plate toggle clasp.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Tiger Eye and Bali Beads
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Tiger Eye and Bali Beads

The tube shaped sterling silver Bali beads in this unique mans bracelet, are handmade by the Balinese artisans in Bali Indonesia.  Complementing these wonderful sterling silver beads are frosted Tiger Eye rounds.  The bracelet  measures 8 1/2" long with a sterling silver S-shaped lobster claw clasp with two sterling disk beads and a large sterling closed ring.

name: Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Red Jasper Tube
description:
Mens Handmade Beaded Necklace - Red Jasper Tubes

These finely polished Red Jasper beads are brick red, with occasional grey, cream, green and bright red colors in random swirls and circles.  Complementing textured metal beads gives this masculine piece its stand-out quality.  Measures approximately 18" and has a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: PMC Necklace – Gothic Explosion Pure Silver PMC Pendant
description:
PMC Necklace – Gothic Explosion Pure Silver PMC Pendant

This round 1 ¼” PMC pendant illustrates abandoned thinking emanating from a solid mass.  The patina finish and 3mm inset natural sapphire enhance the free artistic expression.   This pendant, handcrafted in the Keiden Deisgns studio comes with either a 18" or a 20' snake chain.

name: PMC Pendant Necklace – Elemental Mix
description:
PMC Pendant Necklace – Elemental Mix



This 1 1/8” round PMC pendant necklace blends the wild and  tame as a hand carved floral expression is revealed through the hard elements of life. Select your personal necklace size and style to best display this one of a kind piece. Stamped .999FS.

name: PMC Jewelry - Turquoise Carribbean Drop Pendant Necklace
description:
PMC Jewelry - Turquoise Carribbean Drop Pendant Necklace



As beautiful and relaxing as a glimpse or the Caribbean Sea this small PMC pendant measuring 1" long by 7/8" in width with  turquoise green acrylic inlay is a one of a kind piece, stamped .999FS and comes with your choice of an 16" or 18" sterling silver neckwire or sterling silver snake chain.

name: PMC Pendant Necklace - Abstract Medallion
description:
PMC Pendant Necklace - Abstract Medallion


This 99.9% silver handcrafted pendant has an organic abstract design with a bronze patina finish and raised polished silver highlights.  The pendant measures approximately an inch in diameter and hangs from a double strand of soft chocolate brown leather.  The closure is a sterling silver hook with a 2 1/2" extension chain making the overall length of this handcrafted piece from 18" to 20 1/2".

name: Handmade Sterling Silver and Turquoise Bracelet
description:
Handmade Sterling Silver and Turquoise Bracelet

Handmade sterling silver oval beads are the feature of this simple but stylish bracelet.  Stabilized turquoise round and tube shaped  beads complement the sterling silver and the added heart charm finishes the piece for a modern look.  Measures 7 1/2" long with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: PMC Necklace - Pure Silver PMC Pendant with Sapphire
description:
PMC Necklace - Pure Silver PMC Pendant with Sapphire

A galactic vision of whirls and swirls surround a 3mm natural sapphire.  The PMC pendant is 1 1/8” square with the bail attached to the back.  It features highly polished raised areas contrasting with a brush silver background.  A limited edition piece stamped .999FS.   Select a 16" or 18" sterling silver neckwire or snake chain.

name: PMC Necklace - Carved Rock Art Pure Silver PMC Pendant
description:
PMC Necklace - Carved Rock Art Pure Silver PMC Pendant 

This rock art pendant is 99.9% pure silver.  Hand carved in our studio, this rustic pendant has a textured patina background with a pictographic center symbolizing the endless spiral of life around the sun.  This is a one of a kind piece.  Pendant mounted on a 22" leather cord with sterling silver lobster claw clasp.

name: Handmade Beaded Bracelet - Pearl Elegance
description:
Handmade Beaded Bracelet

Inexpensive but elegant this classic style bracelet is comprised of white and garnet colored fresh-water pearls.  The garnet colored pearls are capped with pretty silver-toned metal beadcaps, and the silver-toned rectangle shaped metal beads with floral design add a touch of elegance to this piece.  The bracelet measures 7 and 3/8" and has a sterling silver lobster "S" shaped clasp with a sterling ring.

name: Gemstone Beaded Necklace - Graduated Turquoise
description:
Handmade Gemstone Beaded Necklace - Graduated Turquoise 

Complement any outfit with this beautiful Turquoise necklace.   These stunning medium blue gemstones graduate larger at the bottom to smaller at the back for a balanced look.  Measures 16 1/2" long with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp and 3" extension chain.

name: Sterling Silver and Turquoise Tube Bracelet
description:
Sterling Silver and Turquoise Tube Bracelet

Simple yet sophisticated, this charming bracelet offers  night time or daytime wear.  Sterling silver curved tubes, about 3/4" long, smooth turquoise round beads with silver tone bead caps and sterling silver round beads team together with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp.  Measures 7" long with a 1 1/2" sterling silver extension chain with a pewter butterfly charm.
